{
  "text": "Before setting the optimal objective function, the observability matrix obs and the controllability matrix con are, respectively, obtained by the expression between Gramian matrix and the system modal energy [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "122166101"
